538
00:45:05,253 --> 00:45:07,187
Zašto me gledaš
tako?

539
00:45:08,356 --> 00:45:09,789
Zašto?

540
00:45:12,226 --> 00:45:13,818
Šta to znači?

541
00:45:14,862 --> 00:45:16,454
Ništa, draga moja.

542
00:45:32,313 --> 00:45:35,578
