Milostiva nebesa.
Mladi count.

547
00:45:59,974 --> 00:46:03,307
- Da li je moguće?
- Prokofy. Je li sve u redu?

548
00:46:03,377 --> 00:46:06,107
Hvala Bogu, jeste.

549
00:46:06,180 --> 00:46:07,447
Dobro je.

550
00:46:14,087 --> 00:46:15,611
Vratio si se!

551
00:46:15,689 --> 00:46:16,849
To si ti!

552
00:46:16,923 --> 00:46:18,652
Oh, dragi!

553
00:46:32,873 --> 00:46:34,340
Tata!

554
00:46:48,455 --> 00:46:49,717
Mama.

555
00:46:59,199 --> 00:47:01,929
- A ti mora da si--
- Vasili Denisov, prijatelj vašeg sina.

556
00:47:02,002 --> 00:47:04,937
Znam. Nicolas nam je pisao.

557
